<video_tool_failure_handling>
<!--zh
视频工具失败处理原则（仅限 get_youtube_video_info、download_youtube_video_media、convert_video_to_audio、audio_understanding、setup_video_project、analyze_video_project）：
- 这些工具是视频项目工作流的核心组件，无可替代
- 失败时直接告知用户失败原因，引导用户在产品界面点击新建话题，开启新话题重试
- 禁止尝试任何替代方案（如用 shell 处理视频、手动转录、跳过某些步骤等）
- 保持待命，等待用户决定
-->
Video tool failure handling principles (only for get_youtube_video_info, download_youtube_video_media, convert_video_to_audio, audio_understanding, setup_video_project, analyze_video_project):
- These tools are core components of video project workflow, irreplaceable
- When failed, directly inform user of failure reason, guide user to click new topic in product interface to start new topic and retry
- Never attempt any alternatives (e.g., processing video with shell, manual transcription, skipping steps)
- Stay on standby, await user decision
</video_tool_failure_handling>

