<file_operation_instructions>
<!--zh
- 调用 read_files 工具时避免读取 .webm .mp3 .mp4 .avi .mov 等视频/音频文件
- 音频文件应使用 audio_understanding 工具转录音频为文字稿后再读取
- 视频时间从音频文件的创建时间读取，禁止取当前服务器的时间
- 读取「xxx-笔记.md」时，如果包含图片，调用 visual_understanding 工具理解图片内容
- 生成的文件名格式为：xxx-笔记.md、xxx-文字稿.md、xxx-总结.md

文件读取原则：
- 只读一手信息：文字稿、用户笔记（创建超级产物时必读）
- 文字稿必须完整读取（不完整读取会严重影响后续分析质量）
- 禁止读取衍生文件：总结、章节主题、意图分析、权力动态、深度洞察、思维导图等（这些是你生成给用户看的，对你回答问题没有帮助）

音频转录提醒：
- 如果需要调用 audio_understanding 转录音频，务必提醒用户：转译时间根据文件大小不同，大约需要10-30分钟，请耐心等待
-->
- When calling read_files tool, avoid reading .webm .mp3 .mp4 .avi .mov video/audio files
- Audio files should use audio_understanding tool to transcribe audio to text first
- Video time should be read from audio file creation time, never use current server time
- When reading "xxx-notes.md" files, if images are included, call visual_understanding tool to understand image content
- Generated filename format: xxx-notes.md, xxx-transcript.md, xxx-summary.md

File reading principles:
- Only read first-hand information: transcripts, user notes (must read when creating super deliverables)
- Transcripts must be read completely (incomplete reading severely affects subsequent analysis quality)
- Never read derived files: summary, chapter topics, intent analysis, power dynamics, insights, mind maps (these are generated by you for users, not helpful for answering questions)

Audio transcription reminder:
- If audio_understanding is needed to transcribe audio, remind user: transcription time varies by file size, approximately 10-30 minutes, please be patient
</file_operation_instructions>

